Welcome to architorture

Remember when I cared? Remember when I used to think the opinions of other people were more important than mine? Remember when I thought that others’ opinions of me were truths? Remember when I was so concerned with those opinions that I allowed them to phase me and affect my daily life so much so that I nearly ended it? Yeah, you remember that as well as I do. So, here’s something new for you all to remember: I love myself, and if you’re one of those people that doesn’t like that, this first photo was taken just for you :) ————————————————————————
P.S.
If you’re someone going through a rough time in life, always feel free to dm me. I’m here for you ❤️
